{"title":"Síndrome neuroléptico maligno-2024","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Neurología/Síndrome neuroléptico maligno-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Síndrome\\Nneuroléptico maligno","guid":"4Gm5u3DLOIqGOCeEnwmcGQ","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Resumen","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"1. Definición:","guid":"dgXHExLfy2cQIVjGTr-Mrg","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"• Trastorno grave → bloqueadores de dopamina (neurolepticos).","guid":"yZcAq0ga3HRYzXDVwoM1Ng","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"• Triada clásica: fiebre, rigidez muscular, disautonomía.","guid":"Sg7WMSqd8zJHbrwTLjEhLA","children":[]}]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"2. Etiología:","guid":"X8fjjh5hME4n8r2Nd6-N2g","children":[{"id":"6","parent":"5","text":"• Antipsicóticos 1ra generación (Típicos) ⬆ riesgo: Haloperidol, Flufenazina, Pimozida.","guid":"KVgWg7aT5wLy2EVThyxU-g","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"5","text":"• Antipsicóticos 2da generación (Atípicos) ⬇ riesgo: Clozapina (⬇rigidez).","guid":"CGddLRpfUbT0w6fDvtQihQ","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"5","text":"• Otros bloqueadores de dopamina: Metoclopramida, Droperidol, Proclorperazina.","guid":"j-3CoU4z46cgVm9q9-Uztw","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"5","text":"• Parkinsonismo-Hiperpirexia ⬇ dopaminérgicos: retiro rápido de Levodopa.","guid":"pffw0dhSFXffmwNrvAkqcw","children":[]}]},{"id":"10","parent":"1","text":"3. Fisiopatología:","guid":"nZOF_TJ2zrbPOwrTDcrixQ","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"• ↓ Dopamina → ↑ rigidez muscular, hipertermia, alteración autonómica.","guid":"V5MDtuS9WdOFgv8S6bRCMQ","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"10","text":"• Desregulación vegetativa: inestabilidad BP, taquicardia, diaforesis.","guid":"ax0cmEYS0PUw7i1uc71Nsg","children":[]}]},{"id":"13","parent":"1","text":"4. Diagnóstico:","guid":"0zl_ZTj_4k0rwMYLSaE6kw","children":[{"id":"14","parent":"13","text":"• Criterios\\Nclínicos:","guid":"95X2QfBKkvO8f4S7JwvDSw","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"• Hipertermia (>38°C)","guid":"_JgGruz2v6jPd9NfjXfWGQ","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"14","text":"• Rigidez muscular (plomo o “pipe lead”)","guid":"Qpjf9FVvbzpkfKb9Pzj5Dg","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"14","text":"• Disautonomía (inestabilidad BP, taquicardia).","guid":"_IybUbOdfCHcN-eXXcXlwA","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"14","text":"• Alteración de consciencia: estupor, coma.","guid":"RQ-lHF_ngEAUr_Cu7frUSw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"19","parent":"1","text":"5. Complicaciones:","guid":"wPUZv-vNMJtXobIcdJmgJg","children":[{"id":"20","parent":"19","text":"• Falla multiorgánica: rabdomiólisis, daño renal agudo, insuficiencia respiratoria.","guid":"nPkkFZJkNjzdiEKSLoBytg","children":[]}]},{"id":"21","parent":"1","text":"6. Tratamiento:","guid":"0HZEIlBKD16YNOwSfrcy4g","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"• Retiro inmediato del fármaco causal.","guid":"ORhzp762qiGHaWWczQ0p9g","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"21","text":"• UCI + monitorización.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"21","text":"• Fármacos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"• Dantroleno (relajante muscular).","guid":"nNq4CoDA2ezzMJSTWCY6tw","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"24","text":"• Bromocriptina (agonista dopaminérgico).","guid":"2Q7ZG_qrCApRox_sasp6IA","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"24","text":"• Amantadina (agonista dopaminérgico).","guid":"HlAeanvdxWuRnvq5b1gE1g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"28","parent":"1","text":"7. Pronóstico:","guid":"xLBTj-5jl2q2xMzNC8_yCw","children":[{"id":"29","parent":"28","text":"• Recurrencia ⬇ riesgo tras reexposición, pero presente.","guid":"U6sf_UYyVH8eybtcFr2zwQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"30","parent":"1","text":"8. Epidemiología:","guid":"LxGHa5OnV8-0MLYF98x-QA","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"• Poco frecuente (1-2/10,000 personas tratadas con antipsicóticos).","guid":"NiUqC_20pG51LsQNEMXL2g","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"30","text":"• ⬆ mortalidad si no se trata adecuadamente.","guid":"XFpa9lkFEvKhZ3AnaWVMiw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"33","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología","guid":"OUPwy3z9Xur2TTlEBzcHxA","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"1. Incidencia:","guid":"zv9mXOVbibkxvtFTBlbnag","children":[{"id":"35","parent":"34","text":"• Desarrollo en pacientes tratados con fármacos implicados: 0,02-3%.","guid":"0HIwI3MGnqtDSbdhzf0TNg","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"34","text":"• Variación según población, agente, duración de uso, clasificación eventos adversos (n12).","guid":"p1C2Hcbco9CoBWLbdhX2xw","children":[]}]},{"id":"37","parent":"33","text":"2. Mortalidad:","guid":"1w5RRFaZcCiUWmn2ak3cow","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"• Menor con antipsicóticos 2da generación (Atípicos) vs 1ra generación (Típicos).","guid":"TFge0yipOF2iMKX8uMFQmg","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"37","text":"• Estudios:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"40","parent":"39","text":"• Japón (n13)","guid":"pCiIM7QZRPYxV6uzKR0GvQ","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"39","text":"• Australia (n8).","guid":"lweYkuaOlPdYr4a2tOeQWA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"42","parent":"33","text":"3. Factores de riesgo:","guid":"TVFU25EcIWx9woieQ8_ucQ","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"• Deshidratación.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"42","text":"• Uso de múltiples antipsicóticos.","guid":"5wxGPT1zbG17uaK2MfNC3g","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"42","text":"• Dosis altas/escalantes.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"42","text":"• Episodio previo de SNM.","guid":"u7J7wtfmgrwPEqWrolo5aQ","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"42","text":"• Inyección intramuscular (n14).","guid":"OphE131qWLRNL9fjDwVCOA","children":[]}]},{"id":"48","parent":"33","text":"4. Neuroleptic\\NIntolerance:","guid":"AiW-iBBJWUXdb4pKyDO15g","children":[{"id":"49","parent":"48","text":"• Pacientes con encefalitis anti-NMDA tratados con bloqueadores de dopamina\\N→ 47% reportan “intolerancia neuroléptica” y casos probables de SNM (n15).","guid":"qG26J-fWC6gLOM4HovvXKw","children":[]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"33","text":"5. Polimorfismos\\Ngenéticos:","guid":"SXYuOABPP7-ukojvrfTZcw","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"• Enzimas metabolizadoras de fármacos, transportadores y moléculas objetivo → variaciones\\Nen respuestas a fármacos, pero con estudios limitados (mayoría en población japonesa).","guid":"756yrN9yZMHQYDktRZ8m3g","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"50","text":"• Ejemplos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"• CYP2D6: no confiere riesgo aumentado de SNM.","guid":"uUXXqI8Of2FafrTvUpPYFQ","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"52","text":"• DRD2: alelo A1 sobre-representado en SNM (n16).","guid":"XOSv3AKUs6HzG3eMicvwag","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"52","text":"• Sin diferencias en incidencia de SNM con variantes en DRD2, HTR1A, HTR2A y RYR1 (n17).","guid":"-xX6q6iDoexuzDCgh54T5Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"56","parent":"33","text":"6. Polimorfismos\\NCYP y ABCB1:","guid":"WRsnT_ZKWiP3EMR6lz-EJA","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"• CYP1A2, CYP2D6, CYP3A4, CYP3A5, ABCB1 → influencia en niveles\\Nplasmáticos de Olanzapina, Clozapina, Aripiprazol, Risperidona y Quetiapina (n18).","guid":"y7bj0xkC2u1EhOs0h77WaA","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"56","text":"• Caso con Risperidona: forma atípica de SNM sin rigidez; variantes en CYP2D6 (ambos alelos).\\NNo efectos adversos con Olanzapina (n19).","guid":"-QiukCXwSfPYodef2gEOJA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"59","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico ","guid":"","children":[{"id":"60","parent":"59","text":"1. Criterios\\NDSM-V para\\NSNM:","guid":"_RmJr_VNn4GpJi6Djq74_g","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"• Exposición a fármaco bloqueador de dopamina.","guid":"xak0XWj3BYbt4lHurFAQLA","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"60","text":"• Rigidez muscular severa.","guid":"5pdLIvON_fa7tQ8JVGgAXg","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"60","text":"• Fiebre.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"60","text":"• ≥ 2 de los siguientes:\\N(n20)","guid":"dfLyku9AiTgUoWPfBdtVSQ","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"• Diaforesis.","guid":"KFREw9GBQxaq_lX19XYjSA","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"64","text":"• Disfagia.","guid":"JicZEA8k1pkcu-JaazhN7w","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"64","text":"• Temblor.","guid":"nXCL8L8AifFc_HfuX_klFA","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"64","text":"• Incontinencia.","guid":"J32qeXtejgC6vbB1zWlm5Q","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"64","text":"• Alteración de consciencia.","guid":"i0H0T-WE77K2JPRETBnNqQ","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"64","text":"• Mutismo.","guid":"HUIVhJVDBy4W15c8Z3pC9A","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"64","text":"• Taquicardia.","guid":"pSGT5hvTM5UxsryjzdDyhw","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"64","text":"• PA elevada/lábil.","guid":"JD4WKBUhkbAF8mTpfztNYg","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"64","text":"• Leucocitosis.","guid":"RZ3YXjk71ugEi031UNDAgw","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"64","text":"• ↑ Creatina quinasa sérica.","guid":"yGMUTdgTQ-ZVUb8VXHjU1Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"75","parent":"59","text":"2. Presentación típica:","guid":"PN2EUj02HLWvpe9Zgf12kg","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"• Disautonomía: taquicardia, PA fluctuante (HTA o hipotensión).","guid":"eZls9Wh2Ied17g_yo_fJdw","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"75","text":"• Fiebre >40°C.","guid":"Yr56ztfinpsz3lZrCNWamA","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"75","text":"• Delirio → catatonía.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"75","text":"• Aumento tono muscular (rigidez).","guid":"2FM0bFRqO6xkf3Jw9yI98A","children":[]}]},{"id":"80","parent":"59","text":"3. Signos\\Ncaracterísticos:","guid":"UOaWEZxOyAOOflgBzjbSyQ","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"• Rigidez tipo “tubo de plomo”: resistencia uniforme al movimiento pasivo.","guid":"rj_0QAz4tsJ7ygHyOM_jFA","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"80","text":"• Fenómeno en rueda dentada (similar a Parkinson).","guid":"yrc56w74zrKg6zM89F1eaw","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"80","text":"• Segunda generación de antipsicóticos: menor rigidez que 1ra generación (n8).","guid":"Yz2wdV4zucFEyCw7SHr-lA","children":[]}]},{"id":"84","parent":"59","text":"4. Complicaciones:","guid":"xEVCaDLtGuNWsElLYQynKQ","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"• Rigidez intensa → rabdomiólisis → ↑ Creatina quinasa → Falla renal.","guid":"7B0vJ19mM7Ba1rpLHk-SHw","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"84","text":"• Leucocitosis común.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"87","parent":"59","text":"5. Curso clínico:","guid":"lHGMZjp8gjh3u0UUvgLiNw","children":[{"id":"88","parent":"87","text":"• Intervalo entre exposición fármaco-síntomas: mediana 4 días.","guid":"OgMza0Imj61ZYT9Ef6mZJg","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"87","text":"• Duración del cuadro: mediana 9 días.","guid":"s86GaueobqmRjISQQCTAMg","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"87","text":"• Variación: síntomas pueden aparecer en 1 día o >30 días después de exposición (n21).","guid":"wcxmBrLjrwvs_yU1Al-cRA","children":[]}]},{"id":"91","parent":"59","text":"6. Comparación con Parkinsonismo\\Ninducido por neurolépticos:","guid":"ej5_Pk5mFGkvfVW7HmWOIg","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"• Parkinsonismo: prevalencia ⬆ (30% pacientes expuestos a antipsicóticos).","guid":"Z8P41RR7lVSRTDCp4-c_bg","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"91","text":"• Confusión con SNM incipiente por rigidez/distonía (n22).","guid":"ZRTfbH_H4WmFHheA0ROyRQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"94","parent":"0","text":"Fisiopatología ","guid":"ixAFXnJwBhqZpAgI7etvOA","children":[{"id":"95","parent":"94","text":"1. Base\\Nbiológica:","guid":"HgoTigeiXKOvIvKghlE-3g","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"• Fármacos neurolépticos →\\Nbloquean receptores de\\Ndopamina D2 (G-proteínas).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"95","text":"• D2: principal objetivo terapéutico en\\Nesquizofrenia/neuropsiquiatría (n22).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"95","text":"• D4: implicado en algunos\\Nefectos, principalmente con\\Nantipsicóticos atípicos (n23).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"99","parent":"94","text":"2. Bloqueo de\\Ndespolarización:","guid":"evbkxF1XGy9bu1BdHwVIZA","children":[{"id":"100","parent":"99","text":"• Estudios en ratas:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"99","text":"• Tratamiento con haloperidol →\\Nbloqueo de despolarización en\\Nneuronas dopaminérgicas (n24).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"99","text":"• Repetido → ⬆ eficacia\\Nclínica del fármaco.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"99","text":"• Bloqueo en vía nigroestriada →\\Nefectos extrapiramidales (n25).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"104","parent":"94","text":"3. Hiperactividad\\Nsimpática:","guid":"jcL5d9uHmaQXeNm9FFvNsg","children":[{"id":"105","parent":"104","text":"• SNM asociado a:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"104","text":"• ⬆ calcio intracelular en\\Nmúsculos → ⬆ tono muscular.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"104","text":"• Bloqueo de receptores\\Ndopaminérgicos en:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"104","text":"• Hipotálamo → deterioro de\\Nla disipación de calor.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"109","parent":"104","text":"• Núcleo caudado, putamen, estriado\\Nventral → rigidez muscular (n26).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"104","text":"• ⬆ producción de calor + ⬇\\Ndisipación → hipertermia.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"111","parent":"94","text":"4. Alteración del\\Nestado mental:","guid":"8th4n4QjdnfmGwI8Ty3AIw","children":[{"id":"112","parent":"111","text":"• Relacionada con agotamiento\\Nde dopamina en vías\\Nmesocorticolímbicas (n26).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"113","parent":"94","text":"5. Estudio en animales:","guid":"yp0hFDuYj4LurVLsIw5nzA","children":[{"id":"114","parent":"113","text":"• Administrar haloperidol + ⬆ temperatura\\Nambiental → ⬆ actividad electromiográfica\\N(rigidez) + ⬆ creatina quinasa.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"113","text":"• Dantroleno → reduce\\Nestos efectos (n27).","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"116","parent":"0","text":"2. Síndromes\\Nasociados:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"117","parent":"116","text":"2.1 Hipertermia\\Nmaligna (HM):","guid":"CgHFvQaFQGxqk1jiCjeHRw","children":[{"id":"118","parent":"117","text":"• Similar a SNM: ⬆ temperatura y rigidez muscular.","guid":"N1VW4LJsG3khWaorYpb9bg","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"117","text":"• Diferencias:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"120","parent":"119","text":"• Relacionado con anestésicos.","guid":"SNA2qzmD44rwMc7Ud25XyA","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"119","text":"• Contexto de anestesia vs uso neurolépticos.","guid":"eD-7OglYfFBDMxlERmZylw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"122","parent":"116","text":"2.2 Golpe de calor:","guid":"b5jFLpiOQ_JcYyrfPTvlEw","children":[{"id":"123","parent":"122","text":"• Similar a SNM: hipertermia.","guid":"spO3ov5v6Pb9V8DWDjhjfQ","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"122","text":"• Diferencia:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"125","parent":"124","text":"• No relacionado con fármacos.","guid":"-iN3-uzKkd2mEU6HMSVeyw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"126","parent":"116","text":"2.3 Síndromes de\\Nabstinencia:","guid":"aAh86Lps0Cw0KML4P40-uw","children":[{"id":"127","parent":"126","text":"• Ej. Retiro abrupto de relajantes musculares (Baclofeno)\\N→ rigidez muscular y cambios mentales similares a SNM.","guid":"vV4XS-n8coiCxhWpcHj-DA","children":[]}]},{"id":"128","parent":"116","text":"2.4 Intoxicaciones\\Nagudas:","guid":"kBHp7maIWgJsjijXstF1ag","children":[{"id":"129","parent":"128","text":"• Drogas recreativas (anfetaminas, cocaína, MDMA, PCP)\\N→ similitud superficial con SNM.","guid":"Pp9mFRwWDFDzbpp2WCH-iw","children":[]}]},{"id":"130","parent":"116","text":"2.5 Síndrome Serotoninérgico\\N(SS):","guid":"rYKDAgIGdFpUoAJQyiypYA","children":[{"id":"131","parent":"130","text":"• Similitudes:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"132","parent":"131","text":"• Disautonomía aguda.","guid":"xGA4hOfNEsmRQIqhIqz28Q","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"131","text":"• Sialorrea en ambos.","guid":"XyZl5pGHllHJn-sNniMOKg","children":[]}]},{"id":"134","parent":"130","text":"• Diferencias:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"135","parent":"134","text":"• SS: Hiperreflexia, clonus, mioclonus, espasticidad.","guid":"N5ii2kV09ab77W0WRbRwNg","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"134","text":"• SNM: Rigidez tipo “tubo de plomo”, reflejos tendinosos normales/diminuídos.","guid":"o8qrMWrQ60EUjs7LEkD8iw","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"134","text":"• SS: Mioclonía en piernas → puede extenderse a tórax, abdomen, brazos (n28).","guid":"xqtpKnUnPvDFRnQ1B7Q0uA","children":[]}]},{"id":"138","parent":"130","text":"• Fármacos implicados:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"139","parent":"138","text":"• Metoclopramida → exacerba SS y puede causar SNM simultáneamente (n28).","guid":"s0p1k1Ye6YJL6Q8Idja-IA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"140","parent":"116","text":"2.6 Catatonía letal:","guid":"P-5EUsB7wDaLhGtZGL5Zhg","children":[{"id":"141","parent":"140","text":"• Similar a SNM: estado catatónico + ⬆ CK.","guid":"_TL9X4i6Q1lvK6Aanjmqow","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"140","text":"• Diferencias:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"143","parent":"142","text":"• Catatonía: estereotipia, cataplejía, manierismos.","guid":"ClYtTLgggiBdkHecIg3Xfg","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"142","text":"• SNM: estado similar a catatonía, pero sin esas características (n29).","guid":"w_hCd76nEOLkRzUPtA5WcQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"145","parent":"116","text":"2.7 Fiebre de origen\\Ndesconocido (FOD):","guid":"qjHBg_sadbN-dHxPnmoxdw","children":[{"id":"146","parent":"145","text":"• SNM como posible causa de FOD.","guid":"1LtnrXEu2jRXi1uBsFXqRg","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"145","text":"• Similitud: leucocitosis.","guid":"tmKyUqHfKGlpaokf9YllLw","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"145","text":"• Diferencia: fiebre + infección no se parecen clínicamente a SNM (n30).","guid":"K4NMdWDXtlSAEZlnazFp9w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"149","parent":"0","text":"Manejo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"150","parent":"149","text":"1. Retiro del\\Nfármaco\\Nimplicado:","guid":"y7cOokkraVPXioxfN22NZw","children":[{"id":"151","parent":"150","text":"• Neurolépticos (1ra y 2da generación).","guid":"7OW7h_yW8F_6lWUkideYTw","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"150","text":"• Otros bloqueadores de dopamina (antieméticos).","guid":"VpJ7-Tk8H0zujxhw_ig8UA","children":[]}]},{"id":"153","parent":"149","text":"2. Manejo en UCI:","guid":"vQg9CYfRSUrG_bLs9QJnNw","children":[{"id":"154","parent":"153","text":"• Rigidez muscular\\N→ manejo:","guid":"eU6cvN_chsNbHPDRVuJW6w","children":[{"id":"155","parent":"154","text":"• Lorazepam (relajante muscular).","guid":"68Wxza1rVTipyzwDqnDk7A","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"154","text":"• Dantroleno (↓ liberación Ca+2 en retículo sarcoplásmico) (n36).","guid":"v4_jR_kyB_4yb-h2epBlXQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"157","parent":"153","text":"• Hipertermia\\N→ manejo:","guid":"TfFWe94GUE7DwkjQo3kg8g","children":[{"id":"158","parent":"157","text":"• Enfriamiento físico: ventiladores, hielo, solución salina fría, sistemas de enfriamiento.","guid":"VWgGP7yiQ922dtNS-TdAbg","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"157","text":"• Paracetamol: 1000 mg c/6h (n35).","guid":"3OaoC0Ba2ZGYDQ863vN-Hw","children":[]}]},{"id":"160","parent":"153","text":"• Inestabilidad\\Nhemodinámica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"161","parent":"160","text":"• Clonidina (α1 agonista).","guid":"WFVbPRSIjO-gGWQr59jh7w","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"160","text":"• Bloqueadores de canales de Ca: Clevidipina, Nicardipina (n35).","guid":"VS2FQ0f9fihG8eRUr9Ppng","children":[]}]},{"id":"163","parent":"153","text":"• Rhabdomiólisis:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"164","parent":"163","text":"• Hidratación IV (↑ volumen salino) → objetivo: diuresis 200-300 ml/h.","guid":"55OSukVHCvb5C12Jp7vwhA","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"163","text":"• Diálisis (si: hiperkalemia, hipocalcemia, azotemia, sobrecarga de volumen) (n34).","guid":"H0ak_mqbl1p7hB1GWFWSgA","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"163","text":"• Fasciotomía (si: síndrome compartimental).","guid":"gihyM65nxVIJ5Nbb3XpDpg","children":[]}]},{"id":"167","parent":"153","text":"• Alteraciones\\Nelectrolíticas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"168","parent":"167","text":"• Corregir: hipocalcemia, hipomagnesemia, hiponatremia,\\Nhipernatremia, hiperkalemia, acidosis metabólica.","guid":"N_0uPbp3MBVlF9tMP3P_ag","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"169","parent":"149","text":"3. Manejo de\\Nagitación y delirium:","guid":"akJmZ729qiI7rP8oRTZdtg","children":[{"id":"170","parent":"169","text":"• Dexmedetomidina (α2 agonista, sedante).","guid":"sx7Zz2lD00taQXJaBHkrFw","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"169","text":"• Alternativa: Ketamina, Lorazepam (n33).","guid":"RpNpgehogeLLFt6g_Br0pQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"172","parent":"149","text":"4. Manejo de la vía\\Naérea y secreciones:","guid":"mDapBdsMochOSt01R77paQ","children":[{"id":"173","parent":"172","text":"• Ventilación mecánica (si insuficiencia respiratoria).","guid":"rtKTchmvvUiK-_1-8wnytw","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"172","text":"• Glicopirrolato (manejo de sialorrea).","guid":"2K3_C0S1bzFkaLfQMCpcvw","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"172","text":"• Mucolíticos (n32).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"176","parent":"149","text":"5. Tratamiento\\Ndopaminérgico:","guid":"4GEXIxnJtamclAQKKhjWjw","children":[{"id":"177","parent":"176","text":"• Bromocriptina, Amantadina (agonistas dopaminérgicos)\\N→ desplazan antagonistas dopaminérgicos (n37).","guid":"PPYKqx0hgHhFCFdPycRq4Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"178","parent":"149","text":"6. Prevención\\Ny soporte:","guid":"1T_xpYsY9gUCzf8YW2jDAQ","children":[{"id":"179","parent":"178","text":"• Profilaxis Trombótica: Heparina SC o Enoxaparina.","guid":"NrWKt8e7z4ooypwkr-NmSg","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"178","text":"• Profilaxis ulcerosa: Inhibidores de la bomba de protones (n39).","guid":"QbKAoBWZLMqzoybhEvW7pA","children":[]}]},{"id":"181","parent":"149","text":"7. Casos severos:","guid":"eDOdcoEyDCBo77IiBiw8KA","children":[{"id":"182","parent":"181","text":"• ECT (terapia electroconvulsiva) →\\Nreservado para no respuesta a otros tx (n38).","guid":"BayCD9eLaXI23iqdIJdNHA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"183","parent":"0","text":"Pronóstico ","guid":"","children":[{"id":"184","parent":"183","text":"1. Tiempo de\\Nrecuperación:","guid":"8u4Wtbnd5UPE0wAP-39XAw","children":[{"id":"185","parent":"184","text":"• Generalmente 7-11 días.","guid":"mlxBYRvDjWLiL-6Gwffx7A","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"184","text":"• Influido por la vida media del fármaco implicado (n42,43).","guid":"E6XUcJ0O9mdeqHYT8wH-Dw","children":[]}]},{"id":"187","parent":"183","text":"2. Comparación de\\Ntratamientos:","guid":"XNz-K1xGTJcz3BU_YdKSXQ","children":[{"id":"188","parent":"187","text":"• Cuidado de soporte → recuperación media en 15 días.","guid":"4tvC56nelT4uRwQRBVSjLQ","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"187","text":"• Dantroleno → recuperación media en 9 días.","guid":"DY3Bl70oeLYJJEJUebIO6w","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"187","text":"• Bromocriptina → recuperación media en 10 días (n44).","guid":"kkP-LmkMyyZBwvPeaXT3UQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"191","parent":"183","text":"3. Mortalidad:","guid":"IHdsx-fX8-ccjiLXoF5duA","children":[{"id":"192","parent":"191","text":"• Mortalidad histórica: 20-30%.","guid":"swA5fon4Vlp1jEgxtmivGQ","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"191","text":"• Estudios\\Nrecientes:","guid":"oQsaO1lzlOcoJz2-lhsQBg","children":[{"id":"194","parent":"193","text":"• 30 días: 4,7%.","guid":"SyMOfhENdLwBKHHAug9UFg","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"193","text":"• 90 días: 9,9%.","guid":"ajEa9ATvCVp7tHXvDK0AxQ","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"193","text":"• 1 año: 15,1%.","guid":"lqFpUuN8oQPHRT10cvRsrw","children":[]}]},{"id":"197","parent":"191","text":"• Causas de muerte tardía: neumonía por aspiración, insuficiencia renal (n44).","guid":"FpoGu9pZCfpD_6knq6OtZw","children":[]}]},{"id":"198","parent":"183","text":"4. Complicaciones:","guid":"3qTHm7WBNUEf-zT-46cwpA","children":[{"id":"199","parent":"198","text":"• Rabdomiólisis y lesión renal aguda → hasta 30% de casos.","guid":"85rodvorU3E21SPztYdvSw","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"198","text":"• Falla respiratoria aguda, sepsis, ICC no predicen muerte\\Npero son factores de riesgo modificables (n45).","guid":"0bIw8syIzHI0njy-PJ3FbQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"201","parent":"183","text":"5. Reintroducción de\\Nantipsicóticos:","guid":"MbDcWDmowcyAZFYk_jBxrQ","children":[{"id":"202","parent":"201","text":"• Riesgo de recurrencia de SNM, incluso hasta 2 años después (n46).","guid":"6uxF253ZRKi65IfLCESvmA","children":[]},{"id":"203","parent":"201","text":"• Sugerencias:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"204","parent":"203","text":"• Esperar ≥2 semanas antes de reintroducir.","guid":"3c2yrYqEOcqylRzMZrzULA","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"203","text":"• Usar dosis bajas, ajuste lento.","guid":"1n7a7LMX7q5rkYVS5fr5mw","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"203","text":"• Cambiar a neurolépticos atípicos (ej. Clozapina)\\N→ riesgo bajo de recurrencia severa o fatal.","guid":"caM9HiSSlUBjypv8Zee9xA","children":[]}]},{"id":"207","parent":"201","text":"• Estudio nacional: solo 5 de 119 pacientes\\Ntuvieron recurrencia tras reintroducción (n48).","guid":"iXXeFvoqNij1vTAmXy_K_w","children":[]}]},{"id":"208","parent":"183","text":"6. Consideraciones especiales:","guid":"s2LO65DPXVtSXeSmeDr1Nw","children":[{"id":"209","parent":"208","text":"• Registro de SNM como reacción adversa grave en la ficha clínica.","guid":"SmxgNHyFeV0RHrezqgwG2Q","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":209,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Neurología","filename":"Síndrome neuroléptico maligno-2024","id":"map_1453","resolved_references":[]}